org.eclipse.stardust.engine.api.runtime

Interface LogEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface LogEntry
extends Serializable
    The LogEntry class provides information about the various messages the Carnot engine is logging into AuditTrail.
    Version:
    $Revision$
    Author:
    ubirkemeyer
